    "Description": "\n        <p>The Great Resignation has made hiring more difficult than ever before. In order to hire someone, you have to attract the right talent and vet them through a hiring process. Then, once they're hired, you have to keep them on your team. That\u2019s the formula\u2014but how can you apply it successfully? In this episode of The EntreLeadership Podcast, we sit down with Ramsey Solutions Chief People Officer Jack Galloway. He walks you through how we attract and retain great talent and how you can too. Later in the episode, Jack takes listener questions about retaining talent and whether hiring slow and firing fast is still a good way to operate in this talent climate.</p> <p>\u00a0</p> <p><em><a href=\"https://www.ramseysolutions.com/shows/the-entreleadership-podcast\"> The EntreLeadership Podcast</a></em></p> <p><a href=\"https://bit.ly/3FcVXZi\">Download the The EntreLeader's Guide to Hiring.</a></p> <p><a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bJOSmi\">Schedule a call with Tim, our producer.</a></p> <p>\u00a0</p> <p>Learn more about <strong>EntreLeadership Events:</strong></p> <p><a href=\"https://www.ramseysolutions.com/shows/summit?utm_source=podcast_entreleadership&amp;utm_medium=podcast&amp;utm_content=summit_podcast_promo&amp;utm_term=entreleadership_bu&amp;utm_campaign=summit_podcast&amp;campaign_id=&amp;lead_source=Digital_Content\"> EntreLeadership Summit</a> | <a href=\"https://www.ramseysolutions.com/shows/ems?utm_source=podcast_entreleadership&amp;utm_medium=podcast&amp;utm_content=ems_podcast_promo&amp;utm_term=entreleadership_bu&amp;utm_campaign=ems_podcast&amp;campaign_id=&amp;lead_source=Digital_Content\"> EntreLeadership Master Series</a></p> <p>\u00a0</p> <p>Learn more about <strong>EntreLeadership Coaching:</strong></p> <p><a href=\"https://www.ramseysolutions.com/business/entreleadership/elite-coaching/self-guided-training?utm_source=podcast_entreleadership&amp;utm_medium=podcast&amp;utm_content=elite_podcast_promo&amp;utm_term=entr